sub_title: Global Initiative Leader Consumer Beauty, Body & Skin Care at Coty
summary:
An Accomplished and performance-driven professional with 11 years of International experience in the fields of Innovation & Project Management and Supply Chain Management in the FMCG, Logistics and Beauty Industries. I am fluent in English and French and basics in German.

Based on my professional experience, I am interested in opportunities in Project, Innovation and portfolio Management roles.
